    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The weight is indeed suffocating. It feels as though my very breath is a struggle against an ocean of grief. If the light only brings more mockery, and the shadows offer only a heavy descent... is there no other way to find the stillness? Is there no sanctuary left for a heart so thoroughly broken?",
